title: [Raining Caves, Tunnel]
description: Oversized and extremely hairy, a fast-moving shadow scampers along the wall and disappears into a narrow cavity.  Darkness is extreme, and intermittent sparkles of silver-blue flecks imbedded in the granite give minimal insight to spacial location.  Wafts of fresh rain sneak past but are quickly overtaken by unpleasant scents that border on noxious.
